mstItem.name: Mysterious Divine Wine
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
This precious wine was brewed over a long period of time to be offered to the gods. It can intoxicate even monsters and demonic beasts.

mstItem.name: Refined Magatama
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A Magatama that possesses faint life energy.
A Magatama is said to be shaped like a crescent moon, a fetus, or even a soul. However, its true purpose is veiled in mystery.

mstItem.name: Phoenix Feather
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Feather from a sacred bird of the Orient.

mstItem.name: Secret Gem of Archer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the immense power of an Archer.

mstItem.name: Proof of Hero
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Proof that you've been acknowledged as a hero.
Many possess it, but they aren't 
conscious of it so they forget.

mstItem.name: Arrowhead of Malice
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
An arrowhead that has bathed in blood, sin, and corruption. It is said to carry a curse that invites disaster.

mstItem.name: Meteor Horseshoe
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A tough horseshoe made of metal from a meteor.
Even if the elements are the same, since it wasn't created on Earth, it has a special role.

mstItem.name: Gem of Archer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the power of an Archer.

mstItem.name: Servant Coin
mstItem.detail:
"Servant Enhancement Material"
 A shard of a Servant's Spirit Origin

mstItem.name: Flaming Oni Lantern Plant
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A lantern plant pod that is so hot to the touch it feels as though it were enveloped in the very flames of hell.

mstItem.name: Magic Gem of Archer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the great power of an Archer.

mstItem.name: Crystallized Lore
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A highly pure crystal of magic created
when human history crosses a stream of Mana.
It can be said that it is the ingredient for materializing Heroic Spirits.

mstItem.name: Tearstone of Blood
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
The crystal of the tear shed by a giant eyeball-like creature when it dies.
A strong curse is residing within this crystal.

mstItem.name: Black Beast Grease
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A fatty tissue collected from the skin of a soul-eating beast.
By repeatedly refining it through distillation and purification, it turns into a high-quality magical resource.

mstItem.name: Archer Piece
mstItem.detail:
"Ascension Material"
A piece signifying the Archer class.

mstItem.name: Archer Monument
mstItem.detail:
"Ascension Material"
A monument in glory of the Archer class.

mstItem.name: Holy Grail
mstItem.detail:
A container said to grant any wish.
Created by the Third Magic, it is said 
that it can materialize those that do not possess forms.
